data.description:
Charming 3-Bedroom, 2-Bathroom Home in Little Elm with Newly Installed Hardwood Floors

Nestled in the picturesque community of Paloma Creek in Little Elm, this delightful 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home offers the perfect blend of comfort, style, and functionality. Boasting newly installed hardwood floors throughout, this property exudes warmth and elegance, making it an ideal sanctuary for you and your family.

Situated in the amenity filled community of Paloma Creek, this property enjoys a convenient location with easy access to schools, parks, shopping, dining, and other essential amenities. It's an ideal place to call home for those seeking a combination of comfort, style, and practicality.

This cute 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home in Little Elm with newly installed hardwood floors represents an opportunity to live in a welcoming and stylish environment. Don't miss your chance to make it your own and enjoy the charm and comfort it has to offer.
